\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
"As you know besides our salary we have been receiving 7.00 dollars per diem. However, new government regulations are going to cut down that sum to something like 2.00 dollars per diem. . .But here's another angle. If by chance I sh
ould be moved from my present locality. . .I would again be entitled to the 7 dollars per diem."}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
