\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 Officers' comments on civilians are almost uniformly unfavorable. Examples:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
