\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 The following quotatio
ns are by enlisted men, all privates or P.F.C.'s, who are first- or second-generation Americans writing to families or friends in America in Spanish, Italian, or Portuguese (extracts translated by examiner). The extracts are fairly typical of all the mail
 of this sort passing through this office. Morale in this group is invariably excellent and these letters are also good from a security point of view. Religious expressions are unusually prevalent in these letters.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12086910 
