\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 6. HEALTH}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 The data on health are almost exactly the same as last week. The only new note encountered was a reference to cases of malaria appearing in the army.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 7. MAIL
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910  
\par Opinion of the mail service is a little less }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 severe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910  than last week, 77% of comments unfavorable as
 against 85% but the generally low opinion is not much improved. These comments on mail are typical of the frequent emphasis of its importance for morales.
\par 
\par "We know that we don't get it all but are mighty thankful for all we do get." (77 Evac. Hosp.).}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
"I received your first mail in North Africa and boy was I glad to hear from you and boy a:a I reading that letter over and over again. I read it every time I have time off. I guess I will read the ink right off of it." (Enlisted man, NATAF).
