\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 8. RATIONS}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 Officers' approval of rations, 91% of comments favorable has increased somewhat over last week (86%) but is still a little below the previous average, about 94%. These fluctuations probably are not sign
ificant. Approval is usually in general terms. Disapproval tends to be more specific:
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 "I don't think I'll want any more stew for a while after I get back from this business. We are so much better off, though than many people in the world, who have nothing to eat. Hope we can start f
eeding them one of these days. I'll divide my share with them." (HQ, 1st F.G.).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 "Told my Dad there were 4. things we boys want over here:
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid6436052 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 1. Steak dinner, ketchup, apple pie and ice-cream.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 2. Women - been months since we saw one and then she wasn't a specimen of feminine pulchritude.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 3. Seconds on the dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 4. One way ticket home." (805 T.D. Bn.).
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11616502 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 "The food is terrible. All the meat you are doing without must be going to the ground officers in back of the lines for all we eat is dr
ied beef, hot dogs, cabbage, or stew. No kidding it's no good." (91 Ftr. 93 Ftr. sq.).
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 "The only thing I complain about here is the food we get. We live mostly on 'C' rations. The boys back on the west coast of Africa who aren't doing a damn thing get good food." (81 Gr., 93 Sq.).
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 9. QUARTERS}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 Approval of quarters continues high, 98% of comments favorable, which is somewhat the hi host yet observed. Previous average was 92.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 10. OFFICERS}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
