\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 Adverse criticism of superior officers is 17% of comments on this topic, still more than the earlier average, 14A but a marked improvement over last week, 32% Despite this frequency of condemn
ation by fellow officers, the most severe criticism seen this week happens to be from an enlisted man:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6436052 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 "As far as I am concerned I am so disgusted with my outfit I don't care to try for anything. . .The officers are so lousy it's a shame to call them 'Sir.'" (Co. A, 2619 Prov. Tr. Bn., 551}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 Shore Regt.).
