\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12086910 References to censorship have become very numerous since the issue of NATOUSA Circular 39. A special memo
randum on these has been sent to the Chief Censor and no comments are included in the present general report. Reference to special factors of security is also omitted here.
\par 
\par CHAS. T. HEREFORD 
\par Captain, Infantry
